Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers\u003C/change>\n\t\t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n\t    \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-17\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-12-08\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag added images\u003C/change>\n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000309_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-10-14\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000309.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-10-14\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"rear\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000309_rear_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-10-14\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000309_rear.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-10-14\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#AA\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003Cspace extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\u003Cgap reason=\"illegible\" quantity=\"1\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">Mariniano\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">et\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">Pa\u003C/supplied>terno \u003Cnum value=\"2\">II\u003C/num>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>Achilleus\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>s Claud\u003Cunclear>i\u003C/unclear>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" cert=\"low\">anus\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>\u003Cspace extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"6\"/>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">\u003CroleName type=\"supracivic\" subtype=\"dominus\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>d\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>omino\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/roleName>\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>n\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ostro\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">Claudio\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Aug\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>usto\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">et\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"undefined\" evidence=\"previouseditor\">P\u003C/supplied>aterno \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">\u003Cnum value=\"3\">III\u003C/num>\u003C/supplied> \u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text after Korhonen 2004 and comparison with photograph\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>Plausibly suggested by Manganaro, followed by Korhonen, to be a fragment of a list of the local colonial magistrates, annually, under the consuls of the year; and so dating to 268-269 CE.\u003C!--commented out pending revision-->\n                    \u003C!--Manganaro rejects Mommsen's sugg. that this marked the start of a letter to Paternus, on parallel of CIL 10.7024 and instead interprets as 'un frammento di albo di magistrati di Catina', apparently accepted by AE. Cf. CIL 10.7044 for a possible second such fr., although Korhonen, who also considers this a plausible interpretation considers 7044 a diff. parallel; notes also a similar inscr. from Taormina fasti as an earlier parallel for the practice (Manganaro, CronASA 3 (1964), pp. 40-41 no. 3. The slight problem is that the coss. listing is in the reverse order from the only other known example (CIL 3.3525).-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mommsen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1883\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650757\">7025\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1989.0341c\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IMusCatania\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Korhonen\u003C/author>\n                         \u003Cdate>2004\u003C/date> \n                        \u003CcitedRange>26\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EUC82DH\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1988\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>43\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RZSFKACR\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1989\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>168 no.33 fig.35\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EZMBJ6GN\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
